":"點止冇左個親人 直頭冇左全世界"},{"pid":"19c0a8bf1e265be2b755f998bcff605bb408de1d","tid":129704,"uid":23107,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T21:09:57.000Z","msg":"第一次，擁有<br />\n第一次，失去<br />\n<br />\n原來絕望喺呢種感覺<br />\n<br />\n如果付出所有，可以翻到過去<br />\n<br />\n嗰結果，仲喺咪一樣？"},{"pid":"ef58b078679bfa5a739f420d900657089115b80f","tid":129704,"uid":86476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T21:09:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家有無試過好愛一個人，<br />\n分手嘅時候，好似失去親人嘅感覺？</blockquote><br />\n係咪因爲你地已經親密到好似家人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以當一分手就好似無左個屋企人咁"},{"pid":"6f16bc3113db682b9a2b5015f6b0924408d14ff0","tid":129704,"uid":23107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T21:11:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大家有無試過好愛一個人，<br />\n分手嘅時候，好似失去親人嘅感覺？</blockquote><br />\n係咪因爲你地已經親密到好似家人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以當一分手就好似無左個屋企人咁</blockquote><br />\n我記得最親嘅家人離世嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n就好似正式分手嘅一刻，再不能見"},{"pid":"ea160e295ee1ac8fd25447823a616a1f3676b14b","tid":129704,"uid":70125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T21:11:55.000Z","msg":"最近呢幾日經歷到...好辛苦<br />\n而佢比我知道係騎牛搵馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59677095bdf756bc10467ed3a59a5336c8beab35","tid":129704,"uid":70125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T21:16:38.000Z","msg":"係呢時候我應該係好憎佢 其實都係<br />\n但del d相好似要用好大既勇氣<br />\n今日又經過同佢玩既地方<br />\n望番d相 我就覺得呢個究竟係咪我認職既佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dea477f3d017c325171447de745efe0a1d8ff023","tid":129704,"uid":86476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T21:17:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家有無試過好愛一個人，<br />\n分手嘅時候，好似失去親人嘅感覺？</blockquote><br />\n係咪因爲你地已經親密到好似家人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以當一分手就好似無左個屋企人咁</blockquote><br />\n我記得最親嘅家人離世嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n就好似正式分手嘅一刻，再不能見</blockquote><br />\n我明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然對方仲生勾勾未死 但同對方就好似死左既屋企人咁 雖然曾經好親密但返唔到去以前"},{"pid":"133d28bd098dcd2ccc0d851a592ea35d8ab74173","tid":129704,"uid":23107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T21:22:26.000Z","msg":"房間依然都係熟悉嘅味道<br />\n<br />\n牆上仍然掛住當日嘅合照<br />\n<br />\n衣櫥裏面嘅嗰套杉失去左佢嘅物主<br />\n<br />\n一直瞓雙人嘅單人床<br />\n<br />\n就只剩下自己 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa3f54072d6933b5ff058a563191ebe036ddb95","tid":129704,"uid":27099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T21:28:33.000Z","msg":"巴打幾歲"},{"pid":"e26d1c029e2934629d90e74a30804e59ac170d67","tid":129704,"uid":23107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T21:34:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打幾歲</blockquote><br />\n二十一，但又如何<br />\n我明將來我會覺得自己好蠢<br />\n但呢一刻我係未經歷過<br />\n我站在現在"},{"pid":"bd4f6e48242d4c53829e519bdcbeb87b9f7904d9","tid":129704,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T22:43:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打幾歲</blockquote><br />\n二十一，但又如何<br />\n我明將來我會覺得自己好蠢<br />\n但呢一刻我係未經歷過<br />\n我站在現在</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去睇下書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d55f96701266850ebf7c348485a820c577cdf0","tid":129704,"uid":23107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T22:44:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打幾歲</blockquote><br />\n二十一，但又如何<br />\n我明將來我會覺得自己好蠢<br />\n但呢一刻我係未經歷過<br />\n我站在現在</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去睇下書<